Maybe thats why they are so comfortable being rude. How can be nasty to someone when you first say good evening can you help me with....and before you can even finish......GO OVER THERE AND LOOK ON THE WALL. ..in the rudest manner ever. And when you check them about the first thing they respo d is do you wanna get locked up....for what??? You're rude unprofessional behavior??!!! Like really???!!

originalText.text: Fascinating. It felt a bit odd going there as a tourist, but it was really interesting to see how the system works. It probably is only interesting if you are interested in law and the Law and Order type of programs.
